{
  "texts": [
    "One participant, for instance, said \"can we just dump a bunch of PDFs into a GPT and get a summary?",
    "And it turns out it wasn't that easy.",
    "It wasn't like plug and play.",
    "But it also was showing some potential.\"",
    "Though some of our participants had evaluated contemporary tools, they still considered them models that had to be customized, as in earlier machine learning, rather than useful as drop-in tools."
  ]
}